readable.content: A group of women in matching uniforms , one of which is speaking . A woman wearing a blue and white uniform with a white and blue hat on with her mouth open near others dressed the same . A young woman with a white and blue hat and uniform yells to others dressed the same . Group of women in blue and white uniforms , in profile , facing offstage . Woman wearing a blue shirt with a white vest and a white cap talking while marching .
